messages.content:
@Msven just watched your savior video! It was extremely well done and I can’t wait to watch your other ones when they come out. Considering how little the community actually understands savior — As far as I know there was no consensus whether savior won b+1 before this video — I think it would be cool to have a savior tournament where savior is in every game. 

There could even be a point system where wins with or against savior are worth an extra point, and losses with an asymmetric savior are worth half a point.

Unfortunately I can’t host a tournament but if you or anyone else can host it I think it would be amazing!
